
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-roll-indus-routing-reqs-06.txt'>
    <title>"Industrial Routing Requirements in Low Power and Lossy Networks", Dust  Networks, Pascal Thubert, Sicco Dwars, Tom Phinney</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-roll-indus-routing-reqs-06.txt</link>
    <description>The wide deployment of lower cost wireless devices will significantly improve the productivity and safety of the plants while increasing the efficiency of the plant workers by extending the information set available about the plant operations.  The aim of this document is to analyze the functional requirements for a routing protocol used in industrial Low power and Lossy Networks (LLN) of field devices.</description>
    <dc:date>2009-06-04T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
